<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَلِلتَّفْصِيل:</span> <span class="c2">(ر: نَفَقَةٌ)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تَسَمُّعٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> اسْتِمَاعٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
